title: (Mon Early Bird) Eddie Takes the Lifeguard Test + Craig Campbell on Opening a Coffee Shop and Performs His Hits!
itunes:title: (Mon Early Bird) Eddie Takes the Lifeguard Test + Craig Campbell on Opening a Coffee Shop and Performs His Hits!
description:
The day has come to find out if Eddie has what it takes to relive his glory days as a lifeguard. He takes on 3 tests live on the air that will determine his skills in swimming and saving lives! Can he complete all three?? Our friend, Craig Campbell stops by the studio. He talks about his new coffee show that he opened up and brings his guitar to play a few of his hits!

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
